      <title>肯尼亚 15% 的基础设施债券税可能会削弱外国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/kenya-s-15-infrastructure-bond-tax-may-dent-foreign-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚政府计划开始对基础设施债券征收高达 15% 的利息税，此举可能会损害这种受欢迎的证券的外汇流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/kenya-s-15-infrastructure-bond-tax-may-dent-foreign-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 13:47:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国假日公路旅行在后疫情热潮中创下历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/memorial-day-road-trips-seen-rising-to-record-in-post-covid-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国汽车协会称，今年阵亡将士纪念日周末，美国将有约 3840 万人上路，这是二十多年来追踪该节日出行人数的数据中最多的一次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/memorial-day-road-trips-seen-rising-to-record-in-post-covid-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 04:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
